WESTERN CARIBBEAN SEA.
COLOMBIA TO PANAMA.
DNC 14.
12 METER S/V SWEETBLUE, WHITE HULL, TWO PERSONS
ON BOARD, UNREPORTED SANTA MARTA (11-14.5N 074-12.3W)
